<h2><img SRC="images/ball_blue.gif" height=14 width=14> General Information</h2>

I obtained my Ph.D. degree in Computer Science from the <a href="http://www.uregina.ca">
University of Regina</a>. 
From 1997 to 2001, I worked at the <a href="http://www.cs.uwaterloo.ca">Department of 
Computer Science</a> of the University of Waterloo first as a post-doctoral fellow and later 
as a research assistant professor. I joined the <a href="http://www.cs.yorku.ca">Department 
of Computer Science (now named Department of Electrical Engineering 
and Computer Science)</a> of York University in July 2001.

